HEADWORD: cloche
<hw>cloche</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>a woman's close-fitting
helmetlike hat.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>a low transparent cover put over young plants to
protect them from cold.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

